---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "SharpLsp - 面向 VS Code、Zed 等编辑器的开源 C# 与 F# 语言服务器"
lang: zh
---

{% set t = i18n[lang or 'en'].home %}

<section class="masthead">
  <div class="platform-lockup" aria-label=".NET 生态系统的独立工具">
    <span class="dotnet-mark" role="img" aria-label=".NET 标志">.NET</span>
    <span class="platform-copy">
      <strong>{{ t.ecosystemTooling }}</strong>
      <small>{{ t.notAffiliated }}</small>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="badge">
    <span class="status-dot"></span>
    {%- if release.available -%}
      <a href="{{ release.url }}" rel="noopener">{{ release.tag }} {{ t.badgeAvailable }}</a>
    {%- else -%}
      {{ t.badgeOpenSource }}
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
  <h1 class="title">一个 <span>.NET 语言服务器</span>。每款编辑器都能用。</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    SharpLsp 是用 Rust 构建的开源 C# 与 F# 语言服务器。由 Roslyn 提供完整 IntelliSense、
    诊断、跳转到定义和重构能力，可用于 VS Code、Zed 或任何兼容 LSP 的编辑器。
  </p>
  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button button-primary" href="/zh/docs/">快速入门</a>
    <a class="button button-secondary" href="https://github.com/Nimblesite/SharpLsp">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">code</span>
      查看 GitHub
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-three">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">terminal</span>
      <h2>支持 VS Code 与 Zed</h2>
      <p>完整 Roslyn 补全、诊断、跳转到定义和内联提示。Neovim、Helix 和 Emacs 支持即将推出。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">functions</span>
      <h2>F# 是一等公民</h2>
      <p>由 FSharp.Compiler.Service 支撑的 F# 语言服务器。功能深度与 C# 对等，不是事后追加。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">lock_open</span>
      <h2>无需订阅。没有锁定。</h2>
      <p>MIT 许可。可在 VSCodium、Open VSX 和任何兼容 LSP 的编辑器中使用。无需 Microsoft 账户。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="ecosystem-strip">
  <p class="ecosystem-label">当前可用</p>
  <span class="ecosystem-name">VS Code</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-sep">·</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-name">Zed</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-sep">·</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-name">Rider</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-sep">·</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-name coming-soon">Neovim <small>即将推出</small></span>
  <span class="ecosystem-sep">·</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-name coming-soon">Helix <small>即将推出</small></span>
  <span class="ecosystem-sep">·</span>
  <span class="ecosystem-name coming-soon">Emacs <small>即将推出</small></span>
</section>

{% include "partials/releases-section.njk" %}

<section class="band">
  <div class="copy-block">
    <h2>C# Dev Kit 的开源替代方案</h2>
    <p>C# Dev Kit 是闭源的，不能在 VSCodium 或 Open VSX 上使用，并且组织使用需要 Visual Studio Professional 或 Enterprise 订阅。SharpLsp 采用 MIT 许可，适用于每款编辑器，并且永远没有许可证限制。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="screenshot-frame">
    <img
      src="/assets/screenshots/vscode-hover-page.png"
      alt="SharpLsp 在 VS Code 中显示悬停文档和解决方案资源管理器"
      width="720"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-three">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">explore</span>
      <h2>跳转到定义</h2>
      <p>在整个解决方案中跳转到符号定义，包括反编译的 NuGet 包和 BCL 源代码。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">psychology</span>
      <h2>补全与悬停文档</h2>
      <p>Roslyn 驱动的 IntelliSense，完整支持 XML 文档注释、签名帮助和重载解析。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">build</span>
      <h2>代码操作与重构</h2>
      <p>重命名符号、提取方法、生成构造函数、批量修复诊断，全都通过标准 LSP 代码操作提供。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">format_paint</span>
      <h2>格式化</h2>
      <p>C# 使用 Roslyn 格式化。F# 使用 Fantomas 格式化。遵循 EditorConfig。适用于每款编辑器。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">error</span>
      <h2>实时诊断</h2>
      <p>在输入时显示 Roslyn 编译器错误和警告。无需单独构建步骤即可在线查看错误。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">view_in_ar</span>
      <h2>NuGet 集成</h2>
      <p>无需离开编辑器或运行 CLI 命令，即可搜索、安装和更新 NuGet 包。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="copy-block">
    <h2>离开 Visual Studio。保留你喜欢的编辑器。</h2>
    <p>Visual Studio 仅限 Windows，并迫使你进入重量级 IDE。SharpLsp 将同样的 Roslyn 语言智能带到 VS Code、Zed 和更多编辑器中，可运行在 Windows、macOS 和 Linux 上。无需 IDE。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="copy-block">
    <h2>在你的编辑器中使用 C# 和 F#。不做妥协。</h2>
    <p>用一个安装命令即可在 VS Code 或 Zed 中设置 SharpLsp。MIT 许可。永远开源。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button button-primary" href="/zh/docs/">安装 SharpLsp</a>
    <a class="button button-secondary" href="/zh/docs/">阅读文档</a>
  </div>
</section>
